5000|$|Eduard Maurits Meijers (January 10, 1880, Den Helder [...] - [...] June 25, 1954 in Leiden) was a Dutch jurist of Jewish background, {{who was the}} {{founding}} father of the current <b>Dutch</b> <b>civil</b> <b>code,</b> the Nieuw Burgerlijk Wetboek.|$|E
